Rockmould Homes Limited has announced the appointment of Wale Agbede as its Marketing and Communications Manager. Rockmould Homes is a Lagos-based luxury real estate company. Agbede, a seasoned broadcaster, and a marketing communications expert, will be responsible for developing and driving the marketing strategy of the company across all operations in Lagos and will oversee the future growth into other strategic locations. He brings with him a wealth of brand management experience and represents a new dawn in the real estate business. Speaking on his appointment, Agbede says he’s looking forward to helping the brand improve its reach. “It’s an exciting time to be joining Rockmould Limited and I am looking forward to leading the brand into new periods of growth, both here in Lagos and beyond. “Rockmould already has a grounded reputation in the market and I am keen to drive forward a framework of activity to build on what has already been a tremendous period for the company.” Rockmould Limited is a full service luxury real estate development company that is focused on providing, financing and servicing high value properties for the ever-buzzing middle class in Lagos.